*.tgz

# Terraform — local state can contain secrets/account data; never commit
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
# Helm downloads dependency charts into a `charts/` subdir of each umbrella
# (argocd/staging, argocd/production, argocd/runtimes/*) on `helm dep update` —
# those are build artifacts, not source. Ignore them WITHOUT swallowing the
# top-level source charts (charts/platform-app, charts/tenant), which a bare
# `charts/` rule wrongly matched (it blocked committing charts/platform-app/_helpers.tpl).
argocd/**/charts/
